the wizards in the AE group with my friends.  I<br>
use Ogre Form to lessen frontal stuns and put<br>
my back to the corner to lessen the jolt and<br>
jarring of being whacked by a particularly resistant<br>
little bugger.  The mobs hop around and yet<br>
with Thunderclap herding, they get coralled into<br>
my corner and are lined up for the slaughter.<br>
I never move the enchanter to chase after mobs.<br>
My job is to stun-stun-and more stun.  I let<br>
the rest of the group herd them to me.<br>
<br>
