we have a blast, and we enjoy great success.<br>
Just last night we had a personal best of 41<br>
mobs, and that made us quite proud of our own<br>
efforts.  So you can see, we aren't the uber of<br>
ubers, and we're still successful.  It just goes<br>
to show that there are different ways to go about<br>
things, and just because someone disagrees with<br>
the way someone else does something doesn't<br>
mean that either is right or wrong all the time.<br>
